data.description: 2 homes on one lot?  Yes please. Live in one and rent the other or use for extended living space when your guests arrive. Main home is a single level 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, spacious yard space featuring an amazing water feature to enjoy while relaxing out on the patio under the pergola. The cottage is a 2 bedroom 1 bathroom with clerestory windows above to let in the natural light. Radiant concrete floors keep it cozy year round. All this in a great neighborhood with the beach to the west and Devils Lake to the east. Schedule your viewing today.
